	‚Ä¢	Restraint (R ‚â•): limiting expansion at genesis‚Ä®‚Ä®
	‚Ä¢	Alignment (A ‚â•): coordination across agents‚Ä®‚Ä®
	‚Ä¢	Persistence (P): survival of the least / most vulnerable subset‚Ä®‚Ä®
